videos.description: SMU's Jarrey Foster gets the dunk off the great pass from Ben Moore
videos.headline: SMU's great passing leads to dunk

videos.description: Tulane's Kain Harris hits a 3-pointer from the corner to help increase the Green Wave's lead over SMU
videos.headline: Harris hits a 3 to pad lead

videos.description: Tulane's Kain Harris throws down the emphatic one-handed dunk over the SMU defender.
videos.headline: Harris with the thunderous dunk for Tulane

videos.description: SMU's Semi Ojeleye hits a 3-pointer to help the Mustangs' offense against Tulane.
videos.headline: SMU's Ojeleye hits 3 to cut into Tulane lead

videos.description: SMU's Sterling Brown makes the layup and draws the foul, giving the Mustangs their first lead of the game.
videos.headline: SMU takes first lead of game with And-1

videos.description: Tulane misses the alley-oop and SMU's Jarrey Foster slams down the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Failed alley-oop leads to jam on the other end for SMU
